reviewText:
I don't understand why people are like this, the game is excellent, the history is perfect, until now i loved it, and i'll keep playing this game.

if you care about history, you'll love this game ;-)

graphics? i don't care about it, i started playing games on atari ;-)

So 5min into the game I can tell, its ♥♥♥♥♥ great. To all those q_q'ers: uhhhh its only 30fps, uhhh it doesn't look good for me: It works 100% perfect for me. If you want to have your super ♥♥♥♥♥ and special hardware and complain bout things not working, you definatly do NOT know how hard a PC port is. I won't discuss that here cause I'd wasting my time anyway.

